1Code (apollosai.dev enterprise fork)
======================================

This product includes software originally developed at the 21st-dev GitHub
organization (https://github.com/21st-dev/1code), an open-source "orchestration
layer for coding agents (Claude Code, Codex)" first published on 2026-01-14.

The enterprise fork in this repository, maintained by apollosai.dev, is being
progressively decoupled from the upstream 1code.dev hosted backend in favor of
self-hosted infrastructure (LiteLLM behind an Envoy Gateway with Microsoft
Entra ID SSO). The original work's architecture, source code, and design are
preserved and attributed here per Apache License 2.0 §4(c) and §4(d).

